outputs.output_descr: This trac funded  project is to support ministry of Local Government to implement District Development Programme, phase 3 (DDP3)

District Development Programme III (DDP III) aims to contribute to the promotion of sustainable and equitable growth in the economy of target districts and to contribute to the alleviation of poverty and the achievement of the MDGs and through replication, achieve a similar outcome nation wide
